{"tid":957460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警超聯】【入波】休班警涉非禮16歲女候審　禁入荔景站100米範圍","createTime":"2018-12-27T04:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T10:52:22.000Z","uid":54337,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a616f5d32760811ccf8b407a3ee88573208672b8","tid":957460,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"休班警涉非禮16歲女候審　禁入荔景站100米範圍<br />\n<br />\n一名16歲少女上月16日早上近8時報案，指在港鐵荔景站月台懷疑被非禮。警方事後拘捕55歲休班警員趙魯光，他被控一項非禮罪，案件今日(27日)在西九龍裁判法院提堂。辯方申請暫時毋須答辯，以待索取案件文件及向被告給予法律意見。裁判官遂將案件押後至明年1月24日再訊，期間被告續准保釋，但不得進入事發的港鐵荔景站100米範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於今年11月16日在港鐵荔景站月台非禮女童X。控方透露，被告涉案後已即時停職。"},{"pid":"15ef41e9147eb3e4ee5c9e3d1ef541c6f53a5fe3","tid":957460,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T04:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181227/mobile/bkn-20181227120717452-1227_00822_001.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181227%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181227120717452-1227_00822_001.html&h=771e16a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d45cf9a5894d34a7756c0055a28178873f9c92","tid":957460,"uid":96939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f34c4fff584b18d33932193a9814b19a6b00f9","tid":957460,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181227/photo/bkn-20181227120717452-1227_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181227121850\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181227120717452-1227_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181227121850&h=75ac4d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n55歲休班警員趙魯光被控一項非禮罪。"},{"pid":"3672bf9c52dcd65b1971546124194f1662d6dbd7","tid":957460,"uid":38143,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"73f34c4fff584b18d33932193